Functionality:Administrators: 
●Are able to log-in with a predefined username and password (a user should be able to be recognized as an administrator)
●Upload/remove items to/from the store. Each item consists of a price, a description, and a picture.Users:
●Log-in to a pre-created account 
●Create/sign-up for an account
●View all items in the store
●Click on items and add them to the cart
●View all items in the cart
●Checkout cart (no payment processing; checking out should simply empty the cart, update item quantities, and redirect the user to the shopping page)

Optional (add these functionalities if you have time): Item Categories
●Each item has an additional field (a category)
●Users can filter items by their category Multiple Picture Upload
●Administrators can upload multiple pictures
●Pictures gradually slide in a carousel on the app as the user views the item